---
title: Crispy Sesame Chicken on itsu Chicken Ramen Brilliant'Broth with Udon, Pak Choi and Sugar Snaps
description: Enjoy a taste of restaurant inspired ramen made with itsu chicken ramen brilliant'broth. Ready in no time, this warming broth is crafted with hints of sesame and chilli. Enjoy with udon noodles, crispy chicken & crunchy sugar snap peas.
